{"id": 1272, "genre": 1001, "title": "你希望你的婚礼长啥样？", "description": "这事完全交给爸妈的后果就是，整个婚礼变成一场大型尴尬展，在魔幻现实主义习俗和自己的想法之间找平衡，你有什么点子？（题图来自：Peter Oumanski）", "record_count": 4654, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161011104621Xqv2iSnV9whkJCFT.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-10-15T17:00:35Z", "options": [{"id": 124672, "content": "不想有太多的传统形式", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737236}, {"id": 124928, "content": "採VR式婚禮", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 771823}, {"id": 128256, "content": "亲友吃顿饭之后果断两个人旅行。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 786631}, {"id": 124673, "content": "自由自在的婚礼", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797050}, {"id": 124929, "content": "不想办", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156854}, {"id": 126465, "content": "我老婆说: 每个人都出4位数以上的份子钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 447053}, {"id": 124674, "content": "就想两个人去趟旅游，不想摆喜酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 739308}, {"id": 124931, "content": "要是有个婚礼策划既便宜又浪漫就再好不过，宴请一些自己不想请的人才是有够累", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796541}, {"id": 125187, "content": "我希望是简简单单 只请最爱的那几个人 ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685215}, {"id": 122884, "content": "不想用传统婚庆包办一条龙，场地布置希望找新的鲜花电商来搞花艺", "image": null, "praise_count": 118, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 124932, "content": "坚决不办", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 566722}, {"id": 125188, "content": "两个人的婚礼 两个人就够了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 798521}, {"id": 124677, "content": "如果可以的话:我们的婚车就是自驾车，我载着她走进殿堂", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797067}, {"id": 124933, "content": "真不想有人打扰烦我们", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797605}, {"id": 124934, "content": "别请那么多亲戚！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296767}, {"id": 125446, "content": "不用喝酒，不用请不喜欢或者不熟悉的人，如果能够旅行结婚就好了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800181}, {"id": 126726, "content": "首先得有人愿意和你结婚，负责一切空谈\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 677594}, {"id": 122887, "content": "影楼婚纱照不是必备选项，搞个头纱旅行跟拍或者拍套日常写真多有趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 439, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 124679, "content": "我们要低调奢华有内涵的结婚，", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797067}, {"id": 124935, "content": "不要喝酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 575287}, {"id": 126983, "content": "来咯哦咯后疯你妹……魔鬼。摸到手机没电了……魔盒、?空难会很忙？饿了歌也好听！来咯哦咯后疯你妹……魔鬼。摸到手机没电了……魔盒、?空难会很忙？饿了歌也好听！来咯哦咯后疯你妹……魔鬼。摸到手机没电了……魔盒、?空难会很忙？饿了歌也好听！来咯哦咯后疯你妹……魔鬼。摸到手机没电了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163983}, {"id": 122888, "content": "能不能不！喝！酒！啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 745, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 124680, "content": "不用尴尬，主题也不是应酬，更不是回收之前的礼金。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 750435}, {"id": 124936, "content": "简单的旅行 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 793134}, {"id": 126984, "content": "来咯哦咯后疯你妹……魔鬼。摸到手机没电了……魔盒、?空难会很忙？饿了歌也好听！来咯哦咯后疯你妹……魔鬼。摸到手机没电了……魔盒、?空难会很忙？饿了歌也好听！来咯哦咯后疯你妹……魔鬼。摸到手机没电了……魔盒、?空难会很忙？饿了歌也好听！来咯哦咯后疯你妹……魔鬼。摸到手机没电了", "image": "img/option/option/201610241402303OLsHnWIZk5C0ecD.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163983}, {"id": 124681, "content": "在森林里", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343696}, {"id": 128521, "content": "在郊外庄园，可以不要闹来闹去的，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814619}, {"id": 124938, "content": "连交往对象都没有，然并卵", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 210567}, {"id": 124683, "content": "只需要两个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 778178}, {"id": 124939, "content": "能不能不穿高跟鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 787451}, {"id": 126475, "content": "拍一些超级嘻哈嗨皮的结婚照!婚礼直接在旅行过程中!去和他见识许许多多不同的人和物，受到他们的祝福!", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803826}, {"id": 126731, "content": "简单就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806165}, {"id": 124685, "content": "那天回來到嗎？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797087}, {"id": 124941, "content": "结婚就行，婚礼长啥样都成，随便爸妈呗爱咋办咋办要把份子钱收回去。我就配合。然后自己出去度假爱咋玩咋玩。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595268}, {"id": 126733, "content": "旅游结婚！！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 803267}, {"id": 133646, "content": "简简单单，不用太大规模", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829195}, {"id": 124686, "content": "朋友小聚，俩人旅行结婚，把钱花在吃喝玩乐上了！就是开心\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717754}, {"id": 125198, "content": "能不能不哭哭啼啼的，能不能不浇香槟塔", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154051}, {"id": 125454, "content": "比起这个 我更想知道 我的老公会是谁额", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800314}, {"id": 125967, "content": "旅行结婚，或者小型室外婚礼?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802826}, {"id": 124944, "content": "在热气球上，然后给我最想不到的惊喜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725445}, {"id": 125200, "content": "办两场吧，一场尴尬应试为了亲戚，一场真诚有爱为了两个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 755606}, {"id": 124945, "content": "和你一起就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797628}, {"id": 124946, "content": "如果爹妈允许，不结婚；\n旅行结婚；", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797632}, {"id": 125202, "content": "在爱琴海边搞个两人婚礼.", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127503}, {"id": 124691, "content": "把离婚典礼放一块儿办了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687513}, {"id": 124947, "content": "新人在台上举行仪式、下面一群人只顾的吃、感觉好傻叉、如果是这样的仪式我宁愿不办;", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797630}, {"id": 125715, "content": "梦幻，那都是梦啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802140}, {"id": 124692, "content": "婚礼不重要，对面漂亮帅气就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 767912}, {"id": 124948, "content": "简单而温馨", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795087}]}